Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.toptica.TopMode, [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:mh-occurred)",
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:latest-mh)"], [
    "(param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:mh-occurred)", '#t',
    "> (param-ref 'laser1:charm:reg:latest-mh)", '"2012-12-01 01:02:01"',
    '> '], sep='\r\n') as tm:
    _date = datetime(2012, 12, 1, 1, 2, 1)
    assert tm.laser[0].latest_mode_hop_time == _date
